properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 17 at 10:00AM EST until January 17 at 10:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
3 to 6 feet.

* WHERE...Portions of Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...Until 10 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM EST THIS EVENING... ...GALE WARNING HAS EXPIRED
